  "title": "EA Personnel (Maid Agency)",
  "description": "<p>You should be proficient and knowledgeable in handling all employer and FDW matters independently.</p>\n<p>EA Personnel / Key Appointment Holder Responsibilities:</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>To handle end to end sales</li>\n  <li>To handle customers enquiries in a friendly and professional manner</li>\n  <li>To understand employer’s requirements</li>\n  <li>To interview helpers and compile their bio-data, experience and job history</li>\n  <li>To match customer's requirements with helper's profiles</li>\n  <li>To recommend most suitable helpers to the employers and close the sales</li>\n  <li>To arrange and conduct interviews between the employers and helpers</li>\n  <li>To prepare all necessary documents required for deployment, including Security Bond, Employment Contract, Service Agreement, Rest Day form, Safety Agreement.</li>\n  <li>To apply for and perform all necessary Work Permit transactions with MOM via WP Online</li>\n  <li>To provide after-sales follow-up and service</li>\n  <li>To mediate between the helper and employer whe</li>\n  <li>To follow up with MOM officers if there are MOM matters that require their advice</li>\n  <li>To make arrangements with MOM for card collection, thumbprints, as needed</li>\n  <li>To handle embassy matters, administrative work and follow-up on billing and payments from clients</li>\n</ul>\n<p>EA Personnel :</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Must have experience with a Maid Agency</li>\n  <li>Must have CEI – Certificate of Employment Intermediaries</li>\n  <li>Strong sales ability, communication and interpersonal skills</li>\n  <li>Able to handle all FDW and employer matters independently</li>\n  <li>Singaporean or PR only</li>\n</ul>\n<p>We offer attractive package for the right candidate. Our company believes in work life balance.</p>\n<p>5 day work week</p>\n<p>Attractive Salary and Benefits</p>\n<p>Send your resume to Maglow75@gmail.com or contact 97200099 for an interview</p>",
